Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍍金的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我一直相信你一定會來救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 能讓亞絲娜登出遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的狀態被複雜的代碼拘禁在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想解除的話必須要用到系統控制台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在研究室看過類似的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有蟑螂混進小鳥的籠子裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…須鄉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界能否別用這名字稱呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我妖精王奧伯隆陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 無法活動自如吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我打算在下次的升級版中引進的重力魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有點過於強大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 桐谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是叫你桐人比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼登上這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才似乎有個奇怪的程序運行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是用這雙翅膀飛來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接問你的大腦就一清二楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會以為我是突發奇想才製造出這種裝置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多達300人的原SAO玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有他們獻身協助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考及記憶操作技術的基礎研究已經完成八成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去無人能做到的直接控制人類靈魂的神技
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會成為我的囊中之物了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多虧了假想世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的一切絕對不會被饒恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰不饒恕我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 這世上不存在神明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 在篡改你們的靈魂之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先舉行一個狂歡派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙 太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然NPC的女人是做不出這種表情的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我費力好大的功夫才再現出現實中的明日奈的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至還把分析機器帶到病房裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我的努力能得到評價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾就老老實實地匍匐在地就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統指令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從等級10變更為等級8
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會階段性地加強痛感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一旦降至等級3以下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實中的肉體似乎也會受到影響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 須鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會因為這點事就受創的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這份尊嚴能保持多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘?1小時?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能給我延長一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我告訴你我現在所想的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡好好享樂一番之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去你的病房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊在大型顯示屏上播放今天的錄像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊和你再一次好好地快活一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你真實的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜 好甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須鄉 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是報應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為在遊戲世界中我是最強的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能憑一己之力救出亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼力量都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是認清了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要屈服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈服於你曾否定過的系統功能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玩家 而他是Game Master
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話可玷污了那場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那場讓我見識了人類意識那超越系統的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我認清了未來的可能性的你我之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種攻擊毫無靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊世界的刀刃可是更加沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人感到更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還存在有奇怪的BUG呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登錄系統
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ID 希斯克裡夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼 那是什麼ID
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統指令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理者權限變更
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ID奧伯隆 等級變更為1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我更高階的ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是支配者 是創造者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個世界的王 是神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是你偷來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論這個世界 還是其中的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不過是在偷來的寶座上自鳴得意的賊王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢…竟敢對我用這種口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統指令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物品ID 聖劍生成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0060,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從我的命令啊 廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是神…這是神的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就了結一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統指令 物品ID 聖劍生成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0240,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一條口令就能召喚傳說中的武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候做個了斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賊王和鍍金的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統指令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將疼痛吸收等級降至為0
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…茅場晶彥無論在什麼場合都未曾畏縮過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茅…茅場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個ID是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼死了也要來妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出一張看透一切的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我想要的東西盡數奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我也不是不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾因敗於他之手而對他俯首稱臣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過要變成他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你施予亞絲娜的痛苦可遠不止這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我都我相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在我也相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論至今為止 還是從今以後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都會是我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會救我於水深火熱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是如此的無力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我會努力變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界大概已經入夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我會立即到病房去見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就希望醒來第一個見到的是桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能回去現實世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}終止服務並退出登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}取消    退出登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種變化準會讓你大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去各種地方做各種事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一切就結束了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡吧 希茲克利夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是 也可以說不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是茅場晶彥意識的回波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦即殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話還是一如既往地深奧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 總之先向你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必言謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無償的善意並不適用於你我之間的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然這總要付出代價的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是世界的種子「The Seed」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待它萌芽之後你就會知道這是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把那時的判斷交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除也可 忘卻也可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你對那個世界存在憎恨以外的感情的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被保存在爸爸的NERVGear的局部存儲器裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經返回現實世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很快就會回來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道這個世界將會變得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的核心程序就存儲在爸爸的NERVGear裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}確定要退出登錄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見你一直沒有回來於是有些擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來晚了真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的很感謝你 小直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有你的話 我什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在哥哥的世界裡幫上哥哥的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把亞絲娜姐姐帶回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她終於…終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定在等著哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜姐姐就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這次我會正式介紹她給你認識

Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:22.54,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高く高く この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.60,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと きっと って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.42,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう一度願うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.07,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とめどない想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.58,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}日常に飲まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.96,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}揺らめきながらまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.69,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}形を変えていった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.39,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今さらもう遅いかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.84,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}返事のない自問自答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.22,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すべてはそう自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:12.53,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}終わりも始まりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:19.74,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高く高く この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:26.91,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}優しい光を目指して羽ばたくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:34.16,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心に灯した情熱を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.30,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと きっと って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.50,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう一度願うから

Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:22.54,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}更高更高向著那蒼穹伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.60,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會默念著承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.42,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再度祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.07,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永無止息的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.58,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被日常所湮沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.96,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在搖曳中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.69,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再次改變了姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.39,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}事到如今是否已太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.84,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我向著虛空自問自答道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.22,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}其實一切都取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:12.53,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論終結還是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:19.74,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}更高更高向著那蒼穹伸出手
